entry.title: Zelensky Says Ukraine Needs More Time Before Launching Counteroffensive
entry.content: Ukraine’s military hasn’t yet received equipment pledged by Western allies and the cost in lives could be too great if it were to proceed now, the president said.

entry.title: Migrant Influx Overwhelms Southern Border as Title 42 Winds Down
entry.content: The pandemic-era border measure that for three years has served as a blunt border-enforcement tool for two successive administrations is set to end on Thursday night.
